# Storage rules for this repository. Mirrors the consuming project's intent for this
# plugin's subtree, with one deliberate difference: this repo uses NO git-lfs (plain blobs
# only) so cloning needs no LFS setup; the consuming project stores the same model files
# under LFS on its side. Do not add filter=lfs rules here.
# Repo-local by design: the sync tooling never copies this file in either direction, and
# no checkout-time text normalization is declared (line-ending handling lives at the sync
# boundary, not here).

# Unreal binary assets (never normalize / diff)
*.uasset binary
*.umap binary
*.collection binary

# Media
*.mp4 binary
*.ico binary

# Vendored embedding model (plain blobs on purpose -- see header)
*.onnx binary
